The Jatizso mine is found just outside the western gates of Jatizso. The mine is accessed from a stairwell just outside the city proper. The Fremennik Isles quest has to be started in order to go in the mine.

It is more dangerous than most mines, as it is inhabited by aggressive ice trolls - male, female and runts in the northern half of the mine. However, it may be worthwhile as players can obtain plenty of mithril and adamantite ores fairly close to a bank, which is located in the city.

Because there is a furnace in Neitiznot and anvils in Jatizso, this mine can be great for miners and smithers.

Gruva Patrull guards the entrance of the mine.

The '''Jatizso mine''' is found just outside the western gates of [[Jatizso]]. The [[mine]] is accessed from a stairwell just outside the city proper. [[The Fremennik Isles]] quest has to be started in order to go in the mine.

It is more dangerous than most mines, as it is inhabited by aggressive ice trolls - [[Ice troll male|male]], [[Ice troll female|female]] and [[Ice troll runt|runts]] in the northern half of the mine. However, it may be worthwhile as players can obtain plenty of [[mithril ore|mithril]] and [[adamantite ore]]s fairly close to a [[bank]], which is located in the city.

Because there is a furnace in [[Neitiznot]] and anvils in [[Jatizso]], this mine can be great for [[Mining|miners]] and [[Smithing|smithers]].

[[Gruva Patrull]] guards the entrance of the mine.
